msgid "How to upgrade to Qubes 4.3"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_3.rst:6
#: c76d04d18d6046e0b263e4df5cbc98f0
msgid ""
"This page explains how to upgrade from Qubes 4.2 to Qubes 4.3. There are two"
" ways to upgrade: a clean installation or an in-place upgrade. In general, a"
" clean installation is simpler and less error-prone, but an in-place upgrade"
" allows you to preserve your customizations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_3.rst:9
#: 7712ec7793b2456e99887638d2fce66c
msgid "Back up"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_3.rst:12
#: 7ec71648dd5e495cad97aad5e4da63eb
msgid ""
"Before attempting either an in-place upgrade or a clean installation, we "
"strongly recommend that you first :doc:`back up your system </user/how-to-"
"guides/how-to-back-up-restore-and-migrate>` so that you don’t lose any data."
msgstr ""

